18.Media Queries
    Media Queries allow CSS to apply conditionally based on device characteristics like screen width, height, or orientation.

    <h2>👉 Media Queries ka use CSS me responsive design ke liye hota hai.
Matlab: screen size / device ke hisaab se CSS change karna.</h2>

<pre>
  /* Mobile */
@media (max-width: 480px) {}

/* Tablet */
@media (max-width: 768px) {}

/* Laptop */
@media (max-width: 1024px) {}

/* Desktop */
@media (min-width: 1200px) {}

</pre>

